description: Returns an array that summarizes each privacy budget template in a specified collaboration.

parameters.name: collaborationIdentifier
parameters.description: A unique identifier for one of your collaborations.

nested_items.name: nextToken
nested_items.description: The pagination token that's used to fetch the next set of results.

nested_items.name: collaborationPrivacyBudgetTemplateSummaries
nested_items.description: An array that summarizes the collaboration privacy budget templates. The summary includes collaboration information, creation information, the privacy budget type.

nested_items.name: id
nested_items.description: The unique identifier of the collaboration privacy budget template.

nested_items.name: arn
nested_items.description: The ARN of the collaboration privacy budget template.

nested_items.name: collaborationId
nested_items.description: The unique identifier of the collaboration that contains this collaboration privacy budget template.

nested_items.name: collaborationArn
nested_items.description: The ARN of the collaboration that contains this collaboration privacy budget template.

nested_items.name: creatorAccountId
nested_items.description: The unique identifier of the account that created this collaboration privacy budget template.

nested_items.name: privacyBudgetType
nested_items.description: The type of the privacy budget template.

nested_items.name: createTime
nested_items.description: The time at which the collaboration privacy budget template was created.

nested_items.name: updateTime
nested_items.description: The most recent time at which the collaboration privacy budget template was updated.
